headline: LRN Corporation Wins Seven Brandon Hall Group Awards
summary: NEW YORK, August 20, 2025--LRN Corporation, a leader in ethics and compliance solutions, won a total of seven awards at the 2025 Brandon Hall Group™ HCM Excellence Awards®, capturing four Gold awards and three Silver awards in the Learning and Development category. This is LRN’s fifth consecutive year being honored by the Brandon Hall Group.
